content: all file types available for editing in {{organizationName}}

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message indicating that all file types are available for editing in a specific organization. It appears in a UI element related to file format selection, likely on a dialog or button that allows users to select an editing option. Translators should provide a message that accurately conveys this information while respecting the organization's name.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrasing "zur Bearbeitung verfügbaren Dateitypen" is awkward and not idiomatic German. A more natural phrasing would be "zur Bearbeitung verfügbar sind".
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: alle in {{organizationName}} zur Bearbeitung verfügbar sind Dateitypen

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "բոլոր հասանելի ֆայլերի տեսակները {{organizationName}}-ում խմբագրելու համար" is a literal translation and doesn't flow naturally in Armenian. It directly translates 'all available file types in {{organizationName} for editing'. A more natural phrasing would emphasize the availability of editing.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: բոլոր ֆայլերի տեսակները խմբագրելու համար հասանելի են {{organizationName}}-ում

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'visi failu tipi, kas pieejami rediģēšanai {{organizationName}}' is a literal translation but sounds awkward in Latvian. A more natural phrasing would be 'visi failu tipi rediģējami {{organizationName}}'.

The translation "{{organizationName}} හි සංස්කරණය කිරීම සඳහා ඇති සියලුම ගොනු වර්ග" is not the most natural or accurate translation of "all file types available for editing in {{organizationName}}". A more natural phrasing would emphasize the availability of editing for those file types within the organization.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: {{organizationName}} තුළ සංස්කරණය කිරීම සඳහා සියලුම ගොනු වර්ග అందుబాటులో ఉన్నాయి
